{"tid":45731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大亞灣核電站驚傳洩漏事故 中共全面封鎖消息","createTime":"2016-12-19T07:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T15:09:09.000Z","uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4ab9f8b75b2b086c97da4050d0fa1c7c08a90f0","tid":45731,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:22:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.epochtimes.com.tw/upload/images/2016/12/12/235512_medium.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.epochtimes.com.tw%2Fupload%2Fimages%2F2016%2F12%2F12%2F235512_medium.jpg&h=48d95cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多家港媒披露，供應香港電力的大陸廣東大亞灣核電站上月發生洩漏，但中共全面封鎖消息。大亞灣核電站曾發生多次洩漏事故，但大多被中共隱瞞，而且從2010年到現在每年給當地居民發放高達10億元以上的封口費。<br />\n<br />\n大亞灣核電廠自建成以來，已發生多起核洩漏事故，僅在2010年就發生了3次，但均被中共隱瞞。<br />\n<br />\n據自由亞洲電台2014年12月披露，大亞灣核電廠2010年發生核洩漏事故後，當局為免村民反核維權，給當地三個鎮約有10萬名原居民，每人每月秘密發放所謂的1000元「生態保護費」，每年高達10多億元，村民反饋直到2014年底還在拿，並說怕新聞界曝光，當局「不讓講」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/12/11/n8582154.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F16%2F12%2F11%2Fn8582154.htm&d=9OMDtgqKsXJWl5qPXZvpZ5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=84fef091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/16/12/11/n8582154.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5c6da52aa8c012f676e249088fa0214b9f626ae5","tid":45731,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:28:06.000Z","msg":"廢老廢中係時候做救國英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b3c2e143f43438877f81de075db8ae4efaf79f","tid":45731,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:29:28.000Z","msg":"支那賤種條命就係賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1000蚊可以連命都唔要重害埋其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3283d6e94c378260ea30e29584d347381564f20f","tid":45731,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T07:30:06.000Z","m